#

Penne Arrabbiata

30 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickSpicyItalian

Description

A spicy and flavorful pasta dish perfect for a quick dinner.

Ingredients

  • penne pasta: 8 oz
  • canned crushed tomatoes: 1 can (15 oz)
  • garlic: 4 cloves
  • red chili flakes: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • fresh basil or parsley: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
